{"3009640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Sakura, The Jirai-kei Magical Girl", "steam_appid": 3009640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sakura, The Jirai-kei Magical Girl》是一款具有選擇項的小說遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤身一人的主人公秋葉創志，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天在繁華的鬧區街頭，遇見了一個穿著地雷系服裝的少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她站在夕陽下，看起來又餓又無助，於心不忍的創志便給她買了些食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沒想到就在那之後，創志突然被一種名為「非人族」的危險存在襲擊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >眼看就要命喪當場時，一名身穿賽博朋克風戰鬥服裝的櫻花髮色少女出現在他面前，擋住了攻擊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「——魔裝啟動。變身（Trance）！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——這是一場在守護變身少女戰鬥的同時，守護世界安寧的浪漫物語——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▶小櫻</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：藤崎 紗矢香</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「洗澡不是每天都要洗的。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras/68e5b5bfc1dbd3ecd7b9473e76555041.avif?t=1737705640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras_big/68e5b5bfc1dbd3ecd7b9473e76555041.avif?t=1737705640 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >國家秘密組織「超常災害對策室」的行動隊員。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不諳世事，極度嫌麻煩，怕生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因為除了戰鬥以外一個人什麼都做不了，所以需要照顧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了戰鬥外，生活中什麼事都做不好，所以需要別人照顧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且，她的食量驚人，每月的伙食費高達一百萬日圓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶椿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV：みたかりん</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「你可以認為我們的對策室是專門負責『UMA』的治安組織。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras/010a536886023ed60cb068e399297931.avif?t=1737705640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009640/extras_big/010a536886023ed60cb068e399297931.avif?t=1737705640 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超常災害對策室的室長。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幾乎不離開本部。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一位穩重且溫柔的女性領導者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶秋葉 創志</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某次意外中成為小櫻的專屬「監護人」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天生熱心腸，對需要幫助的人無法袖手旁觀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用E-mote技術打造流暢的角色動畫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多條分支路線結局（ED）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精美劇情CG </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Staff</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色設計：おやずり</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇本：あま味かぼちゃ</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >製作人：しながわ二郎</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sakura, The Jirai-kei Magical Girl》是一款具有選擇項的小說遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong